:

1. *Šalim* se sa svojim prijateljima svakog vikenda (I joke with my friends every weekend).
2. On često *šali* svoje učenike (He often teases his students).
3. Ona je skoro uvek u dobrom *šalu* (She is usually in a good mood).
4. On voli da *šali* oko situacija (He likes to joke around situations).
5. Ona je često *šala* o svojim problemima (She often joked about her problems).